              <li>ì´ë ‡ê²Œ ğŸ‘‰ void drawHouse(<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">const RGB&amp; roof_color, const vec2&amp; pos, const float&amp; angle = 0.0f</code>)</li>
